            . I am a <rs id="t17680224-20-viclabel120" type="occupation">pawnbroker</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17680224-20-victim213 t17680224-20-viclabel120"></join>, and live in <placeName id="t17680224-20-crimeloc121">St. John's-street</placeName>
