             pawned these stays about eight o'clock in the evening on the 1st of January, with me, for half a guinea.</p>
               <p>Toole's defence.</p>
               <p>I was taken up wrongfully at first; I am a <rs id="t17680224-20-deflabel122" type="occupation">brick-maker</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17680224-20-defend209 t17680224-20-deflabel122"></join>, a hard working lad.</p>
